# Donald Trump Origin Story - YouTube Short

This plan outlines the process of generating a highly-paced, 90-second YouTube Shorts video detailing Donald Trump's origin story utilizing Remotion. It will use the provided API keys for Text-to-Speech and leverage `youtube-shorts-mastermind` principles.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The Voiceover generation script will use the provided ElevenLabs key. I will utilize the `with_timestamps` endpoint to generate high-quality, word-level synced captions in `.json` format to power `@remotion/captions`.

> [!IMPORTANT]  
> The script is tuned to ~140 words to fit the exact 90-second target with dramatic pauses and pacing. Do you want to review the script draft before we execute the voiceover generation?

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Pre-Processing Scripts
We will create scripts out of the Remotion root to handle media and audio fetching.

#### [NEW] [scripts/generate-voiceover-trump.ts](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/remotionVideos/scripts/generate-voiceover-trump.ts)
- Will contain the 5-6 scene 90-second documentary script.
- Uses ElevenLabs `with_timestamps` API using the `eleven_multilingual_v2` model and provided API key `sk_6c...`.
- Saves `.mp3` audio and parses `alignment` data into Remotion-compatible `Caption[]` arrays `captions.json`.

#### [NEW] [scripts/copy-media-trump.ts](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/remotionVideos/scripts/copy-media-trump.ts)
- Maps the necessary assets from `media-source-about-donald-trump` skills into `public/trump-origin/` to be used with `staticFile()`.
- Assets planned to copy:
  - Fred Trump Desk photo
  - Fred & Donald 1987 photo
  - Young Trump headshot
  - NYMA uniform photo
  - Commodore hotel / Trump Tower references

---

### 2. Remotion Code Implementation

#### [NEW] [src/TrumpOrigin/Root.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/remotionVideos/src/TrumpOrigin/Root.tsx)
- Sets up `<Composition>` for `TrumpOriginShort`.
- Integrates `calculateMetadata` (from `remotion-calculate-metadata`) to dynamically adjust video length to exact audio frame count.

#### [NEW] [src/TrumpOrigin/Main.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/remotionVideos/src/TrumpOrigin/Main.tsx)
- Contains the main `<Series>` flow splitting into multiple overlapping scenes.
- Applies loud audio, heavy bass cuts, and non-linear transitions.

#### [NEW] [src/TrumpOrigin/CaptionPage.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/remotionVideos/src/TrumpOrigin/CaptionPage.tsx)
- Reuses mapping from `remotion-captions` to display highlighted text.
- Overhaul with `youtube-shorts-mastermind` kinetic typography rules (hostile easing, extreme bounciness) on word active state.

#### [NEW] [src/TrumpOrigin/Scene.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/remotionVideos/src/TrumpOrigin/Scene.tsx)
- Renders the image assets with aggressive scale / panning.
- Adds noise grains, light leaks, floating elements.

## Open Questions

1. Do you want any specific background music track layered, or should I generate a chaotic/ambient sound, or no BGM?
2. Are you ok with a standard dramatic, deep Male voice from ElevenLabs for the documentary narration?

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run `npm run dev` and analyze the browser using the Browser subagent.
- Run `npx tsx scripts/generate-voiceover-trump.ts` and verify files are output in `public/voiceover/trump-origin`.
- Run `npx tsx scripts/copy-media-trump.ts`.
- Run `npx remotion render TrumpOriginShort out.mp4` to ensure it successfully builds the final 90-second `.mp4`.
